General.Name: Clavister Holding AB (publ.)
General.Description: Clavister Holding AB (publ.), together with its subsidiaries, develops, produces, and sells cybersecurity solutions in Sweden, rest of Europe, Asia, and internationally. The company offers network security solutions, identity and access management solutions, solutions for mobile device and laptop clients, and security management solutions. It also provides cloud services; and professional services, such as installation and deployment, configuration and optimization, and yearly health check services. It serves various industries, including energy utilities, transportation, public administration, cloud and datacenter services, education, defense, public safety, healthcare, communication service providers. was founded in 1997 and is headquartered in Örnsköldsvik, Sweden.
